Keep Track of Items in Jeopardy

Set up criteria for alerts to let you know when a fulfillment step is taking longer than expected to complete. You can set up when it’s in jeopardy and when it’s late. The steps are added to a list and appear in a different color in the Fulfillment Plan Viewer.

Where: This feature is available in Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.

How: To configure jeopardy settings, from Setup, in the Quick Find box, enter Fallout and SLA Settings.
title: Fulfillment Jeopardy Settings in Salesforce
